{
  "texts": [
    "They first transformed the original problem into a universal optimization problem and then developed a DRL-based algorithm to deal with it.",
    "Elbir et al. [254] developed an AI-based hybrid beamforming design for THz-ISAC systems.",
    "Specifically, they leveraged a CNN to estimate the angle of the target followed by another CNN for hybrid beamforming design.",
    "The AI-based approach can achieve comparable performance to the model-based counterparts with much lower complexity.",
    "Considering practical systems with hardware imperfections, Wu et al. [48] developed a DL-based receiver for THz-ISAC systems, which consisted of one sensing network and one communication network."
  ]
}